sentences: Gary Lawyer (born 1959) is an Indian singer-songwriter known for his works predominantly in Western Music & Bollywood.
He started his career as a nightclub singer in New York City.
He is the first Indian to be signed for a western album outside India and the first English music video "nights on Fire" to be played on MTV in India.
Today he is known in India as "the man with a golden voice".
